{"type": "article", "id": 24607, "title": "空气净化器", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-29T06:59:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 64, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607162854aOjiAs3dI12VKEZ7.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">来自旧金山的设计工作室 Carity 发明了一个同名的空气净化器。将风扇安装在花盆上，就可以将净化后的空气排出了。花盆中内置 WiFi 模块可以及时将信息发送到智能手机的软件上，监测空气质量和湿度，并控制风扇的转速。产品目前正在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/628579643/clairy-the-most-amazing-natural-air-purifier?ref=project_link\">这里是众筹链接</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607162852GjzqXaFscnxwCIeL.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071628523GnzPhpCyBAewNWa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73594132\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607162853jypB23fo0HucPbVC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73594132\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071628534pRukCr8eXtzHZYK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73594132\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607162854mf2NvAHkWB7MLOtQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73594132\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}